FORRT Contributor Analyses

Last updated on May 10, 2025

As of 11 May 2025, FORRT has a total of 86 completed or ongoing projects and support teams, with a total of 573 contributors. There is an average (mean) of 2.43 contributions per person across all FORRT projects, and the average number of contributors per project is 15.92.
